Token.Abstract: This protocol defines the interface to the SBBScheduleManager's non-constructor, non-initializer methods. The interface is abstracted out for use in mock objects for testing, and to allow selecting among multiple implementations at runtime.
Fetch the list of Schedules for the user from the Bridge API.

Parameter.Name: completion
Parameter.Abstract: An SBBScheduleManagerGetCompletionBlock to be called upon completion.

ReturnValue.Abstract: An NSURLSessionTask object so you can cancel or suspend/resume the request.
